ons"}],"verses":[{"id":"rectxADPfXt5TO2uv","ref":"Gen.15.1","text":"After these things the word of the LORD came unto Abram in a vision, saying, Fear not, Abram: I am thy shield, and thy exceeding great reward.","year":-1911},{"id":"rec0FzgbBMBqMR1hH","ref":"Gen.15.2","text":"And Abram said, Lord GOD, what wilt thou give me, seeing I go childless, and the steward of my house is this Eliezer of Damascus?","year":-1911},{"id":"recn3EKGZy4c7IMcs","ref":"Gen.15.3","text":"And Abram said, Behold, to me thou hast given no seed: and, lo, one born in my house is mine heir.","year":-1911},{"id":"recZXNpwFBAp9KnEC","ref":"Gen.15.4","text":"And, behold, the word of the LORD came unto him, saying, This shall not be thine heir; but he that shall come forth out of thine own bowels shall be thine heir.","year":-1911},{"id":"recSeTbrwk9mBzdkl","ref":"Gen.15.5","text":"And he brought him forth abroad, and said, Look now toward heaven, and tell the stars, if thou be able to number them: and he said unto him, So shall thy seed be.","year":-1911},{"id":"recDjNhckL4ZjkFwR","ref":"Gen.15.6","text":"And he believed in the LORD; and he counted it to him for righteousness.","year":-1911},{"id":"recO9ELUt5Djwq15z","ref":"Gen.15.7","text":"And he said unto him, I am the LORD that brought thee out of Ur of the Chaldees, to give thee this land to inherit it.","year":-1911},{"id":"recvt9idKLBeQ5XBB","ref":"Gen.15.8","text":"And he said, Lord GOD, whereby shall I know that I shall inherit it?","year":-1911}]}
